in your player.java search for oh dear you are dead! you SHOULD see this or something like it teleportToX = 3254; teleportToY = 3420; //pEmote = 15; //pWalk = 13; sendMessage("Oh dear you are dead!"); setSkillLevel(3, 99, playerLevel[3]); currentHealth = 99; hitDiff = 0; updateRequired = true; appearanceUpdateRequired = true;
NOTE THIER WILL BE TWO OF THESE 1 WHEN U DIE AND RESPAWN AND 1 WHEN U LOGG INTO SERVER! change the teleportToX = 3254; and the teleportToY = 3420; too where u want to come back when u die and 1 when u logg into server (find out by looking at them)
